Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Immigrants to America and assimilation
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjgn7
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 29 May 1998
What happens if immigrants to America don't want to become Americans? Alistair Cooke considers assimilation, patriotism, Memorial Day and proposition 227.